sequenceDiagram
    actor Approver
    participant API as Award API<br/>(FastAPI)
    participant SB as Service Bus<br/>award-events topic
    participant AUX as Auxiliary App<br/>(event dispatcher)
    participant WP as Workday Proxy<br/>(ACA)

    Approver->>API: Approve nomination
    API->>SB: publish AwardApproved<br/>{ nominationId, employeeId, amount }
    API-->>Approver: 200 OK · status = Approved

    SB-->>AUX: AwardApproved event<br/>(payout-orchestrator subscription)

    AUX->>WP: POST /payouts<br/>{ nominationId, employeeId, amount }
    WP-->>AUX: 202 Accepted<br/>{ paymentRef: "WD-2026-00123" }

    AUX->>API: PATCH /nominations/{id}<br/>{ status: PaymentSubmitted,<br/>  paymentRef: "WD-2026-00123" }
    API-->>AUX: 200 OK

    Note over WP: simulated processing delay<br/>(real Workday: payroll cycle)

    WP->>API: POST /api/webhooks/workday/payment-confirmed<br/>{ paymentRef: "WD-2026-00123", status: accepted }
    API-->>WP: 200 OK
    API->>SB: publish PayoutAccepted<br/>{ nominationId, paymentRef: "WD-2026-00123" }

    SB-->>AUX: PayoutAccepted event<br/>(payout-orchestrator subscription)

    AUX->>API: PATCH /nominations/{id}<br/>{ status: Paid }
    API-->>AUX: 200 OK
